  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Just as the waves flow towards the shore,</l>
            <l>So does life come to its end,</l>
            <l>Making place for new people to live,</l>
            <l>And it happens suddenly, without us realising.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>When a human is born, he <choice><orig>get</orig><reg>gets</reg></choice> all the attention,</l>
            <l>His main goal being to grow up,</l>
            <l>When grown up, life comes back at him,</l>
            <l>And is surprised by what it created.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>With time, one's enthusiasm fades away</l>
            <l>and one does not see anymore of life's beauty,</l>
            <l>forgets his own uniqueness,</l>
            <l>and waits for his inevitable death.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>And although life is cruel,</l>
            <l>I hope you know my love and appreciation for you.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
